===Proposed internationalized ccTLDs=== {{Main|Proposed top-level domain#Internationalized country code top-level domains}}
== {{anchor|ICANN}} [[ICANN]]-era generic top-level domains == * Name: DNS name * Target market: intended use * Restrictions: restrictions, if any, on who can register, and how the domain can be used * Operator: entity the registry has been delegated to * IDN: support for [[internationalized domain names]] (IDN) * DNSSEC: presence of DS records for [[Domain Name System Security Extensions]]
