{{update|date=July 2013}} [[Image:Chad Prefectures numbered 300px.png|right]]
[[Chad]] was divided into 14 [[prefecture]]s from 1960, the year of independence, to 1999, when the country was divided in [[departments of Chad|28 department]]s:
A further reorganisation in 2002 divided the country into the current 18 [[Regions of Chad|regions]].
