[[Niue]] requires its residents to register their [[motor vehicle]]s and display '''[[vehicle registration plate]]s'''.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.worldlicenseplates.com/world/PA_NIUE.html|title=License Plates of Niue"|website=www.worldlicenseplates.com}}</ref> Current plates are [[Vehicle registration plates of New Zealand|New Zealand standard]] 360 mm × 125 mm, smaller in height and width than Australian plates<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.autographics.co.nz/nz-frames|title=NZ Number Plate Frames|website=www.autographics.co.nz}}</ref>, and use New Zealand stamping dies, as zeroes now have a slash through them (e.g. 52Ø9). {|class="wikitable" |- !Image !First issued !Design !Slogan !Serial format !Serials issued !Notes |- |[[File:Niue license plate graphic.png|150px]] | | | | | | |- |}
